Danielle,

PIRA had two agreements in place with Enron.  The first was with Enron
Global Markets, which received the following PIRA Services:

- North American Natural Gas Retainer Service
- North American Electricity Retainer Service
- Global Oil Retainer Service
- European Natural Gas Retainer Service
- Emissions Market Intelligence Services (EMIS) - NOX /SO2/CO2 coverage
- Natural Gas Liquids (NGL) Forecast - covering U.S./Europe
- Daily Electricity Demand Forecast
- Western Canada Crude Price Forecast and PADD II Balances report

PIRA served the following four offices:

